&lt;h1 id="for-potential-phd-students"&gt;For potential Ph.D. students&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Over the next few years, I may take on a few additional Ph.D. students, although times may come when I&amp;rsquo;ll be too full (e.g. a time that ended recently). This page is intended for those considering working with me, although it also contains some tips for graduate students in general, as well as an idea of what I expect.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>